data: Yee-ha! Them Zaibatsu don't know what hit 'em! Here's $30,000. Keep this up and you could end up one of the Good Ol' Boys. An' there's always plenty work for them, Rooster.
Hey, Rooster! Billy Bob Bean here. I'm real pissed with the Zaibatsu and SRS troublin' us so I want you to make 'em trouble each other. Go steal a Zaibatsu Z-Type.
Get your ass back in that wired vehicle, boy!
The Zaibatsu have barricaded the key access point to their territory. Gettin' rid o' the barricade could be helpful in the future.
The clock's tickin'! Get ya ass outta the Pickup, Rooster - she's gonna blow!
Arm the explosives with your trigger finger, Rooster, but don't hang around.
That was silly, Jumbo. Now I'm never going to be a Loony with a Limo.
Well done! You did it, baby!
No no no! You cannot save your state of play while you are on a job. Get back to work!
OOH! That's lights out for the bonkers mad Loonies!
Cool, Jumbo, but I still can't get a ride. We need to create some chaos so steal another Taxi.
Get that Taxi crushed, Jumbo - you know you want to.
No time for fare dodging, Jumbo. Get back in the Taxi and get on with the job.
That ain't no Water Taxi, Jumbo.
Is this what they call a River Taxi?
Shit, Jumbo, it's too late - the bastards are on to us! The job's off for now.
I'm sick of Yakuza interference. Kill the tattooed scum!
Yes, Gecko! That's one less piece of Yakuza shit!
That was resourceful, Gecko, but one car's still at large!
People can always be replaced but secrets cannot. Excellent work, Gecko - well worth $60,000.
Hey, Gecko! Our Latin Biologist Doctor Cubana is being tortured for information in one of two Yakuza cars circling the city. Destroy the cars, before he squeals.
Get out of the Cop Car, Gecko, and let the crane take over.
Take Shady to the Zaibatsu Car Crusher in North-East Zarelli.
Come on, Gecko, sound the horn!
Now drive to the Train Station!
This is no time to play around, Kosai.
Hiroshi will not come out until the two City Bank Guards are out of the way. What are you waiting for, Kosai?
Stay in the car, Kosai! I will advise you.
Kosai! Get back there and sound the horn!
ZitZaki is important to us! Get back in the car!
Doctor ZitZaki is wary of strangers, Kosai. Sound the horn so he knows it is safe.
Hoo-hoo! We Loonies respect people who like killing Yakuza poops.
Tell your friends! The Zaibatsu Corporation is interested in offering contract work to anyone prepared to keep the Loony population to a minimum.
That wasn't so smart, now was it?
Try life in the big city on your own, ya worthless piece-a-shit!
Hey there, stranger! Welcome to the Downtown District. Stick around if you wanna learn what's going down...
Getting arrested wasn't so smart, Jumbo.
The J-Lab is history and the Loonies are safe in insanity. You are one real cool cat, Jumbo. Maybe we do business some other day. For now, here's $40,000.
Cool shootin', Jumbo! Plant the explosives in his place.
You will die in J-Lab, Loony!
Maybe you ain't so crazy, Jumbo, 'cos those hitmen are all history. Here's $40,000.
A Yakuza escaped, Jumbo, so you be the bitch with no job.
Nicely done, Jumbo! You NAILED his bitch ass.
Look, Jumbo, you HAVE to use a Yakuza Miara for my plan to work.
Steal a Yakuza Miara and drive over to the Zaibatsu quarter - then run over Trey Welsh's top three Z-Lieutenants. Ha ha ha!
Welcome to Yakuza Town, Jumbo! Happy hunting!
Shit, Kosai! That Tank means business.
Deliver Gama Rei to the Safehouse NOW!
What are you doing with the Medicar, Kosai? You have a job to do!
Hi, Kosai, it's Johnny Zoo. Gama Rei has to leave the City Hospital - fast. He's in plastic surgery so you need a Medicar.
My dream car! Wasted! Stay away from me for a while, Jumbo.
Very cool, Kosai. Bring it to my garage.
Lance! Dead! That's the job over for you, Jumbo.
The guard outside the Cop Car Compound is too nice to die. Get some wheels and meet Lance - he will distract the Guard for $1,000 a pop.
Hello, Elmo's special friend. I have arranged for a gun and some bombs to be left behind the Harman Hotel. I'd like to come but it's bath night.
You will find it difficult to do business now that he is dead, Kosai.
Good, you have enough dollars to arm the Ice-Cream Van. Get to it!
We ain't payin'! Die, Yakuza delivery boy!
Sound your horn, Kosai, the Loonies are expecting you.
Hi, Kosai, it's Johnny Zoo. The Loonies still owe me money for merchandise. Get some wheels, get to the City University and GET MY DOLLARS!
Now go pick up the Z-Men.
Stop wasting time, Gecko. Go get the Z-Men!
The Dementia's rigged! Get your ass back in the car and drive cool to the Loony Garage.
The traitor and his men must die! Kill them all, Kosai!
Three down, one to go. Come on, Gecko - move it!
Dead Dealers are no use to anyone - least of all me, Gecko.
Hey, Gecko! Trey Welsh here. The Yakuza are flooding the streets with cheap merchandise. I need you to supply my dealers - FAST. Collect the new shipment and get moving!
That wasn't so smart, Gecko. The job's OFF.
Get back in the Bank Van, dumb ass!
Give the package to the Cop - with our thanks!
Get the Bank Van and the clean cash back to the Safehouse - FAST!
Pick up the Z-Men Unit - then I will fill you in on the job.
You have a short memory. You already took this Zaibatsu job and made a mess of it.
You are already on a Zaibatsu job. Return only when your work is done.
The Yakuza have no respect for you! Disappear!
You expect the Zaibatsu to respect YOU?
You need more respect to work for the Yakuza!
I told you to use a Miara.
I told you to use a Z-Type.
Congratulations! You completed all the Zaibatsu jobs!
I ain't touchin' that! Get outta here!
Shit! What a waste of time that was!
Way to go! You did it!
You made a stupid mistake, Kosai!
You failed me at a critical time, Kosai! You are OFF the job.
Remember, Gecko - a Zaibatsu in custody never talks.
Well you certainly made a mess made of that!
How can you pick them up from there?
Hey, Gecko, how can you steal the Bank Van from there?
Get back and crush that Taxi!
Where are you going? Pick up Gama Rei!
Stop fooling around and meet those Loonies!
Get back and do the deal!
I hope fer your sake the Cops are in a good mood, Rooster.
Use this Vehicle to shoot 75 people in 90 seconds!
Bad luck, buddy! You blew it!
That takes care of the Zaibatsu Corporation!
Kill people for points before the time runs out!
That was an... interesting way to quit the job, Grasshopper.
Ah, Grasshopper! Such a pity to see you fail like this.
The Kovski are looking for this Limousine - it was stolen only a few hours ago!
Make sure Target Two dies, Gecko!
The target will be waiting for your Hot Dog Van, Gecko. Note that these hot dogs are poisoned...
He was a top Zaibatsu Operative, Gecko. You cannot do this job without him.
Good, Gecko. Now meet another Z-Operative - he has lethal merchandise for you.
Hi, I was told to meet you. You stay right there while I load up the hot dogs!
Success, Gecko! You need a Hot Dog Van to execute the second part of this job.
My apologies, the trigger was stuck. Stand back!
HA HA! Now I kill Uno Carb and all his silly little boys!
Excellent, Gecko, you have the Special Package. Be VERY careful - it is highly unstable.
Hey, Gecko, it's Uno Carb. I need you to neutralize THREE Key Operatives from rival outfits. First you need to collect a Special Package...
Emergency! Someone's made it past the guards!
This area is restricted! No questions!
Move fast, Gecko! Bring the Tank back to my Garage!
You have excelled yourself, Gecko. Park this Bad Boy in my Garage!
You have Zaibatsu style, Gecko. Deliver this vehicle to my Garage.
My son wants to deal with this Informant. Steal a Cop Car and I will relay to you further instructions.
Zaibatsu Agent Kappa has target in sight!
Zaibatsu Agent Alpha has target in sight!
Ha! Zaibatsu Assassins are a joke!
Fantastic, the doorway is open! Find my Kovski!
You got the right to become silent!
Hey! Do you have Security Clearance?
You killed my comrades! You will die!
How did you get in here? DIE!
Excellent, you are inside, Gecko. Now steal back my AI Brain Unit Truck.
Satchmo was getting old anyway. Now steal a Kovski Bulwark and try to enter using Zaibatsu stealth!
My intelligence was poor - the back door is also locked. I will program Satchmo The Safecracker to meet you. Get moving!
This Jefferson is special, Z-Man. You will have to die!
Get back in the Cop Car and park it, Gecko!
Cool, Gecko! Head for the Zaibatsu Power Core Crane and deposit your cargo.
Get back in the Truck Cab and get to the Crane, Gecko!
The car is on the island near the Docks, Gecko. The only available access is via these rooftops.
Where are you going, Gecko? Get back in a Bulwark and back to the Krishna quarter NOW!
Good. Now drive to the Krishna quarter and run down some little orange people.
You want a little anarchy, Z-Man?
Look, man, I'm being tailed. I can't talk. My mute handler will pass you the green.
The Russian Mafia hate the Capitalist Zaibatsu! Kill the Zaibatsu and we will respect you.
Welcome, Comrade, to the Russian Mafia!
Jerkov won't be pulling fast ones ever again!
That's Uno Carb plugged for good!
OUTSTANDING! You wasted all three Bosses! Shit, that's gotta be some kinda achievement!
Congratulations, Gecko! You have succeeded in completing ALL the Zaibatsu jobs!
I knew you were up to the job, Comrade!
You are playing Russian Roulette with the big boys now!
The Tanks are cheap Western trash! Destroy them and protect my new Kovski Cars!
Top Karma Assassin Nova Bright lies in wait in an Armored Bus. Eradicate him, Comrade!
Outstanding, Comrade! You helped the Karma Assassins to meet their maker!
This is getting tense, Comrade! Only TWO Assassins remain!
One final Krishna Killer to kill, Comrade!
Good work, Comrade. Now there are only FOUR Hitmen to hit!
Another Krishna bites the dust, Comrade! Now there are SIX to kill!
At last we are doing great street business - thanks to you, Comrade. We will work together again I am sure. For now, here is $40,000.
I think next time we use them for hot dogs and save the motor car.
Get out, Comrade. Your role in this job is almost over.
I wonder how long these Z-Dealers can hold their breath? Let's find out... Take them to the Crane!
Is it that time already? Shit, I ain't even sold out yet. Oh well...
Like, here it is and here you are, man. Far out!
The first Z-Dealer is waiting at the Train Station in Bayano, Comrade.
Good work, Grasshopper. Let us crush a few more Cop Cars to drive the message home.
Where are you going, Comrade? Get back in the Cop Car and get to the Lubyanka Docks NOW!
My son is waiting with a few of my men at the Lubyanka Docks. Take the Informant to him.
Now take the Bus across to Maharishi and pick up some Krishna.
Get back in the Hot Dog Van!
Please don't take me! I'm all saturated fat!
Our savior! We are weak... We need the power of the Krishna Karma Bus!
Check that my loyal Krishna are still converted.
Never send a Tank to do a man's work!
Praise you, Grasshopper, the defenses are destroyed! Now help the Krishna to escape.
Another Tank disabled! Krishna is smiling, Grasshopper.
Impressive, Grasshopper! You annihilated a Tank!
Grasshopper! Sunbeam here. Loyal Krishna are being held as Zaibatsu Guinea Pigs. You must save them before Deconversion Drugs have their effect!
It is imperative that you plant the bomb where the guard was standing.
I trust you will enjoy watching the results of your labor, Grasshopper.
Fantastic, Grasshopper! Now plant a bomb where the dead guard was standing.
I'm gonna convert you, Krishna - from living to dead!
It seems that our path is blocked by danger, Grasshopper. Only you can clear a way!
I'm gonna blow your ass to Tibet!
Grasshopper! Sunbeam here. We need to convert strong Russian Workers. Steal a Truck from Lubyanka Warehouses and head for Mad Island Docks. Beware - the guards are vicious.
Thanks to you, Grasshopper, the Russian Workers are saved! Have $60,000 with our love.
Be calm, Grasshopper - the Unconverted are coming!
The Truck is destroyed and your job is terminated, Grasshopper.
How did you possibly manage to fail?
How did you possibly manage to pass?
Stand back, shorty, while I open this Gateway.
Okay, shorty, show me the Gateway.
The Zaibatsu do not negotiate with the Krishna!
We do not do business with the likes of you.
This is the Russian Mafia zone. Kill some Zaibatsu if you want a job!
Be calm - you have made a mess of this job already.
Displease the Krishna and your end will be nigh!
Only one Krishna task at a time, Grasshopper! You are already on a job.
Use a Tank to destroy 20 vehicles in 60 seconds!
HEY! You now have enough cash to leave this District. Follow the marker if you want to leave!
So you can handle a SWAT Team. But do you have what it takes to steal a Special Agent Car, Gecko? Go for it!
Be warned - we do not tolerate those who dare cross our path.
Mess with us and we will screw you up!
Come back when we got good reason to respect you more!
You already took this job and made a mess of it!
Who are you? You are advised to leave this area and return only once you have killed some Zaibatsu scum.
You know where to go, Gecko. Now park it!
Park the Cop Car, Gecko. I'm looking forward to playing Cops And Robbers. Ha ha ha.
What are you doing? This car is OURS.
Super, Gecko! My Z-Technicians will have the Flamethrower attached in seconds.
Bring the Fire Truck to The Village!
OK, Gecko, here's the deal - steal a Cop Car.
Holy shit, Gecko! What a BANG! What a BLAST! Have $30,000 for a job well done.
She's gonna blow, Gecko! Get out of the Pickup!
Complete your job, Gecko. Park the Pickup beside the Clone Test Center.
Excellent, THC-303. Now all you need to do is destroy the Generator and the H2000 Water Company will have to call in the plumbers! Ha ha ha!
It's a pleasure to watch you work, THC-303. You deserve this $70,000.
This SRS Traitor must also die!
Ah, just what I need - a Taxi.
Sheesh, City Boy, you got lead in your ass? Get outta here!
Well done, THC-303. Now go to the Ol' Banjo and collect Gran'pa.
Congratulations, THC-303. I can see your talents developing under my auspices. Here is $30,000 for your hard work.
THC-303 you imbecile. Now we are on the verge of a gang war.
Now be careful, THC-303. Bring them all back to the Scientist Research Center - and fast.
Okay, boys, get on the Bus - and no spittin'!
Efficient and effective work, THC-303. Here is $30,000. Spend it productively.
Ooh, is there a party going on in here?
Get out of the car, THC-303, and watch the Zaibatsu die!
About time! Here is my Z-ID.
Well done, THC-303. Now find the third Z-Man.
Taxi! You are early. Where are the others?
Do not leave the Taxi, THC-303!
SHIT! We got a RIOT on our hands!
I heard you got some Beany Liquor for me?
GodDAMN, Rooster! Get your ass back into The Village.
You sure got a taste for it, Rooster! C'mon, let's do the Zaibatsu. Head over to The Village. Yee-ha!
Rooster! Billy Bob here! Me an' the boys are lookin' fer fun down SRS way. You bein' a Good Ol' Boy an' all you wanna join in the fun? First to destroy five Meteors is The King!
They guard that Army Base real well, Rooster. You get what I mean!
C'mon, Rooster - one killer to kill!
What an UGLY son-of-a-bitch! Five to kill, Rooster!
Hell, it's Hitman Season! Six to go!
Yee-ha! We got Zaibatsu killin' Scientists and Scientists killin' Zaibatsu... You sure are The Man, Rooster! Have $30,000 fer yer fine work.
